high_descs: Go to the nightstand on the left of the bed
Grab the phone off of the nightstand
Turn around and go to the nightstand on the right of the bed
Put the phone in the top drawer
Turn around and go to the table
Grab the phone off of the table
Turn around and go to the nightstand on the right of the bed
Put the phone in the top drawer
anns.task_desc: Putting two phones in a drawer on a nightstand

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the nightstand to the left of the bed.
Pick up the phone off of the nightstand.
Turn around and walk towards the door, hang a left after the bed and walk over to the wall then turn left and walk up to the nightstand to the right of the bed.
Open the upper drawer of the nightstand and put the phone inside in the front left corner then close the drawer.
Turn around and walk over to the table against the wall.
Pick up the phone off of the table.
Turn left and walk over to the window, then hang a left and walk up to the nightstand.
Open the upper drawer of the nightstand and put the phone inside to the right of the phone that's already in there and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two phones into the upper drawer of a nightstand.

high_descs: Walk to the night stand to the left of the bed.
Pick up the cell phone to the right of the lamp.
Walk to the night stand to the right side of the bed.
Open the top drawer, place the phone inside of the drawer, close the drawer.
Turn around and walk over to the desk.
Pick up the cell phone behind the alarm clock.
Walk back over to the night stand on the right side of the bed.
Open the top drawer, place the cell phone inside of the drawer, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To move two cell phones to the night stand drawer.
